002 ==> 286034 : digikam icons conflicts with oxygen-icon-theme
003 ==> 286165 : Tag hierarchy not preserved when exporting metadata to IPTC.
004 ==> 285742 : Crash in setup.
005 ==> 243074 : Channel mixer hangs on initialize.
006 ==> 124814 : No color temperature used for RAW images.
007 ==> 285194 : digiKam crashing while scanning >20000 pictures.
008 ==> 

